<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mini Netflix - Lecteur</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #141414;
            color: white;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.7) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%);
            padding: 20px;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .back-button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background-color: rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.9);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .back-button:hover {
            background-color: #e50914;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.2);
        }

        .back-button svg {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 80px auto 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .video-container {
            background-color: #1f1f1f;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #e50914;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        video {
            width: 100%;
            max-height: 80vh;
            background-color: black;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 10px;
            }

            .video-container {
                padding: 15px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <a href="/" class="back-button">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
            </svg>
            Retour à l'accueil
        </a>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="video-container">
            <h1>Lecteur Vidéo</h1>
            <video controls>
                <source src="/uploads/<%= filename %>" type="video/mp4">
                Votre navigateur ne supporte pas la lecture de vidéos.
            </video>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 